OL,3,CBlue cards and sin bins to be delayed
OL,4,Cafter talks with Fifa
OL,6,FAll these are currently yellow card
OL,7,Foffenses, but under the proposed new
OL,8,Frules, players would face being sin-
OL,9,Fbinned and would have to spend ten
OL,10,Fminutes in the technical area.
OL,12,F'It doesn't sound like a fantastic
OL,13,Fidea in the first moment, but I don't
OL,14,Fknow when the last time they had a
OL,15,Ffantastic idea these guys if they ever
OL,16,Fdid, I am 56... never.'
