OL,6,FThe IFAB, the governing body that
OL,7,Fdetermines the laws of the game of
OL,8,Fassociation football, was set to
OL,9,Fpublish protocols on Friday in an
OL,10,Feffort to improve participant
OL,11,Fbehaviour, including trials for a sin-
OL,12,Fbin.
OL,14,FSin-bins have been trialled
OL,15,Fsuccessfully at grassroots level and
OL,16,Fare now set to be tested
