OL,6,FHowever, during the initial trial
OL,7,Fphase, top-level competitions will not
OL,8,Fbe involved. This is to avoid
OL,9,Fconfusion among players ` for instance
OL,10,Fif their domestic league ran a trial
OL,11,Fbut a continental competition they
OL,12,Fwere involved in at the same time did
OL,13,Fnot.
OL,15,FIt is not precisely clear what level
OL,16,Fthe new protocols will be stress-
OL,17,Ftested at initially.
