OL,3,CBlue cards and sin bins to be delayed
OL,4,Cafter talks with Fifa
OL,6,FIt is understood referees will use
OL,7,Fblue cards to indicate a player must
OL,8,Fgo to the sin-bin.
OL,10,FSin-bins will be used for two specific
OL,11,Foffences ` dissent and tactical fouls,
OL,12,Fsuch as Giorgio Chiellini's tug on
OL,13,FBukayo Saka in the Euro 2020 final.
OL,15,FPlayers will be ordered to go to the
OL,16,Ftechnical area for ten minutes. If a
OL,17,Fplayer has already been booked, a blue
OL,18,Fcard will mean they are sent off. Two
OL,19,Fblue cards will also result in
OL,20,Fdismissal.
