OL,6,FWhat other measures are the IFAB
OL,7,Flooking at?
OL,9,FAs well as sin-bins, competitions will
OL,10,Fhave the option to trial 'captain only
OL,11,Fzones'.
OL,13,FThese are to be used by referees when
OL,14,Fthey feel threatened or intimidated
OL,15,Fand mean that once the zone has been
OL,16,Fcreated, only team captains should
OL,17,Fenter.
